PrecisAppointment of RICHARD J. DAW of St. John's, Newfoundland and Labrador, selected from a list of nominees submitted by the Province of Newfoundland and Labrador, to be a director of the Board of Management of the Canada Revenue Agency, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years.
